## 🧪 Getting Started

To run this project locally:

1. **Clone the repository**

```bash
git clone https://github.com/bishopkbb/Ajibade-portfolio.git
```

2. **Open `index.html`** directly in your browser:

```bash
open index.html
```

> No build tools, packages, or frameworks required!

